                    <physDesc>
                        <objectDesc>
                            <supportDesc>
                                <support><p>Fragment of a thick slab of a fine dense grey stone. Lower edge intact. Possibly part of the right edge also intact. Broken left and above, and at the extreme lower right corner; however the cut-away lower right appears to be respected by the text, and the edge has the same finish as the other edges, so may be original. Edges and rear finished roughly. Some mortar preserved on right edge. Original width was greater than 30 cm.</p>
